---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy policy | AGRILENE"
  description="Privacy policy and personal data processing on agrilene.fr — GDPR."
  noindex={true}
>

  <section class="bg-paper py-16 md:py-20">
    <div class="container max-w-3xl">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-ink mb-10" style="font-family: var(--font-display)">Privacy policy</h1>

      <div class="space-y-8 text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-ink mb-3" style="font-family: var(--font-display)">Data controller</h2>
          <p>
            <strong class="text-ink">AGRILENE</strong><br/>
            Maule, 78580 — Yvelines, Île-de-France, France<br/>
            <a href="mailto:contact@agrilene.fr" class="text-green hover:underline">contact@agrilene.fr</a> —
            <a href="tel:+33682077693" class="text-green hover:underline">+33 6 82 07 76 93</a>
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-ink mb-3" style="font-family: var(--font-display)">Data collected</h2>
          <p><strong class="text-ink">Via the contact form:</strong> first name and last name, email address, phone number, company/organisation (optional), enquiry type, message.</p>
          <p class="mt-2"><strong class="text-ink">Via browsing:</strong> anonymous audience measurement data if an analytics tool is enabled.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-ink mb-3" style="font-family: var(--font-display)">Purposes</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1">
            <li>Responding to commercial, technical and distribution enquiries</li>
            <li>Managing client and partner relationships</li>
            <li>Improving the website and its content</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-ink mb-3" style="font-family: var(--font-display)">Legal basis</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1">
            <li><strong class="text-ink">Consent</strong>: for processing data submitted via the contact form</li>
            <li><strong class="text-ink">Legitimate interest</strong>: for relationship management, security and website improvement</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-ink mb-3" style="font-family: var(--font-display)">Recipients & processors</h2>
          <p>Form data is sent by email to AGRILENE via <strong class="text-ink">Web3Forms</strong> (form submission service). The site is hosted by <strong class="text-ink">Cloudflare</strong>. These providers may be located outside the EU (United States); transfers are governed by appropriate safeguards (standard contractual clauses). [To be confirmed based on final providers]</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-ink mb-3" style="font-family: var(--font-display)">Retention period</h2>
          <p>Messages are kept for the time required to process the request, then archived/deleted [period to be specified, e.g. 3 years after last contact].</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-ink mb-3" style="font-family: var(--font-display)">Cookies</h2>
          <p>This website does not place advertising cookies. If audience measurement is implemented, we favour a cookie-free solution (e.g. Cloudflare Web Analytics). [To be confirmed based on tool chosen]</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-ink mb-3" style="font-family: var(--font-display)">Mana app</h2>
          <p>If the Mana app collects data (plant photos, user account), a specific processing notice applies. Details will be provided in the app's own terms and conditions. [To be completed]</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-ink mb-3" style="font-family: var(--font-display)">Your rights</h2>
          <p>Under the GDPR, you have the rights of access, rectification, erasure, objection, restriction and portability regarding your personal data. To exercise these rights:</p>
          <p class="mt-2"><a href="mailto:contact@agrilene.fr" class="text-green hover:underline">contact@agrilene.fr</a></p>
          <p class="mt-2">You may also lodge a complaint with the relevant supervisory authority in your country. In France: <a href="https://www.cnil.fr" rel="noopener" target="_blank" class="text-green hover:underline">cnil.fr</a></p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-xs text-muted/60 border-t border-ink/8 pt-4">
          This page should be reviewed by a legal professional before going live. Last updated: June 2026.
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
